---
title: Mexican-Style Chicken Parmigiana with Creamy Corn & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: A dinner classic with a Mexicana-inspired twist! Our zingy Mexican Fiesta spice blend gives this panko-crumbed parmi a flavourful kick, with a crunchy cucumber, mixed leaf and corn salad to round it off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-style-chicken-parmigiana-178b25c0.jpg
